{"title":"向日葵与墙（外一首）","authors":["陈新巨"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":6,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵与墙（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈新巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿亮如痛苦的日轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿亮如颤栗失落的受伤之月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们这片敏感的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被熏染的血红色快慰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植根于丰厚黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见自己的手在风中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想要抓住什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一堵墙与很多堵墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多墙的土地上姓名被保存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全感良好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在围墙之内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被墙体压迫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭动面颊，总是张望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为渴望中的风光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知道墙外是什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太想知道墙外是什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳破碎火焰流淌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰是神话的舌头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色彩是光线的情愫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙体是历史的肚皮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如火如荼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在神话之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在阳光之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"某个早晨，终于发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被墙体层层包围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重叠叠坚厚高峻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低下头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始不惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝壳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反射月之光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和那晕美丽的雨虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在死亡之后，那翅膀垂下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那铠甲卸下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦如泥沙沉积"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠在哪串项链上辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水如透明之梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折射阳光并被阳光调制成血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知水底下的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知拧灭的那盏灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百千年后成为礁石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝壳死亡是珍珠的再生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水流干涸是河流的解脱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只能看见那倒影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只能看见芦苇与藻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只能告诉我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以外的那些事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡之后再度光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投七彩于雨之青帏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半神话，一半暗示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我游离于河道，在拐弯处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受大地的指使"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}